<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.1.6">
<l>puṟamaṟak kaṭṭikkoṇṭiru valviṉai yāṟkumaikkum</l>
<l>muṟaimuṟai yākkaipukaloḻiyak kaṇṭu koṇṭoḻintē</l>
<l>ṉiṟamuṭai nāltaṭantōḷ ceyyavāyceyya tāmaraikka</l>
<l>ṇaṟamuya lāḻiyaṅkaik karumēṉiyam māṉṟaṉṉaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have ended up seeing him for myself so that entering a body time after time stops,</l>
<l>which treads [me] down with two [kinds of] strong karma, tying [me] completely up outside:</l>
<l>the lord with colourful four broad arms, red mouth, read lotus eyes,</l>
<l>[his] palm with a discus that toils for dharma, [and] a black body.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
